# Ignore compiled APKs except maybe if we want to commit fast-file-share.apk?
# Typically, built binaries are not committed to git repositories, but we want to make sure. Let's ignore *.apk except we can add an exception or ignore it fully. The user said: "now i will compile using github i will push to https://github.com/VarshuAi/fast-file-share".
# So they want the source code pushed, and the APK compiled here. We can ignore *.apk in .gitignore.
*.apk

